LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF IDAHO
Sixty-eighth Legislature First Regular Session - 2025
IN THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
HOUSE BILL NO. 284
BY WAYS AND MEANS COMMITTEE
1 AN ACT
2 RELATING TO THE STATE BUDGET; AMENDING SECTION 67-3506, IDAHO CODE, TO RE-
3 QUIRE THE EXECUTIVE BUDGET DOCUMENT TO BE DELIVERED BY A CERTAIN DATE;
4 AND DECLARING AN EMERGENCY AND PROVIDING AN EFFECTIVE DATE.
5 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Idaho:
6 SECTION 1. That Section 67-3506, Idaho Code, be, and the same is hereby
7 amended to read as follows:
8 67-3506. GOVERNOR TO TRANSMIT BUDGET DOCUMENT. Not later than five (5)
9 days following the convening of each regular legislative session On or be-
10 fore December 1, the governor shall transmit to the legislature a budget doc-
11 ument setting forth his financial plan for the next fiscal year, and having
12 the character and scope set forth. The budget document shall consist of four
13 (4) parts, the nature and contents of which are set forth in section 67-3507,
14 Idaho Code. The requests of the legislative and judicial departments shall
15 be transmitted as submitted by those departments.
16 SECTION 2. An emergency existing therefor, which emergency is hereby
17 declared to exist, this act shall be in full force and effect on and after
18 July 1, 2025.

